Cook with what you have!
Frigo Magic is a mobile application that suggests delicious recipes based on the ingredients you already have at home.
How it works
🍎
Input your ingredients
Tell Frigo Magic what's in your fridge and pantry.
👨‍🍳
Get personalized recipes
Discover recipes tailored to your available ingredients.
🍽️
Cook and enjoy
Follow the simple instructions and enjoy your meal!